  "title": "Harbour Craft Steersman",
  "description": "<p>Job description :</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Operate and navigate boats safely and efficiently</li>\n  <li>Ensure safety of all crew and equipment onboard</li>\n  <li>Conduct routine maintenance and inspection of the boat to ensure it is in good condition.</li>\n  <li>Provide regular update to operations in charge on the boat condition and maintenance</li>\n  <li>Adhere to all safety protocols and company policies</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Valid MPA Steersman (Port Limit) license</li>\n  <li>Excellent navigational and boat handling skills</li>\n  <li>Able to start work in short notice</li>\n  <li>Minimum 2 years experience in operating SR vessel</li>\n  <li>Experience in operation Singapore Port limit Harbour Craft</li>\n  <li>Working experience in commercial diving company will be an advantage</li>\n  <li>Ability to work flexible hours or on Sunday/Public Holiday</li>\n  <li>Well organized and punctual</li>\n  <li>team work</li>\n  <li>Able to work in team</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>",
